&lt;h3 id=&#34;分析a和v_out&#34;&gt;分析$A$和$V_{out}$&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
V_{in} = V_{GS}, V_{out} = V_{DS} \\\
\\ V_{out} =
\begin{cases}
V_{DD} &amp;amp; V_{in} \lt V_t \\
V_{DD} -\frac{1}{2}k_n (V_{in} - V_t)^2 R_D &amp;amp; V_{in} \ge V_t \\
V_{in} - V_t &amp;amp; V_{in} - V_t = V_{out} \\
V_{DD} - \frac{1}{2} R_Dk_n[2(V_{in} - V_t)V_{out}- V_{out}^2] &amp;amp; Triode \ Region
\end{cases} \\\
\\ 如果V_{in}很大, V_{out} \ll 2(V_{in} -V_t) \\\
\\ \begin{aligned}
V_{out} &amp;amp;= \frac{R_{on}}{R_{on} + R_D}V_{DD} \\
&amp;amp;= \frac{V_{DD}}{1 + k_n R_D(V_{in} -V_t)}  \\
( R_{on} &amp;amp;= \frac{V_{out}}{i_D},i_D = k_nR_D(V_{in}-V_t)V_{out} )
\end{aligned} \\\
\\ \begin{aligned}
A_v &amp;amp;= \frac{\partial V_{out}}{\partial V_{in}}\\
&amp;amp;= -g_m R_D  \\
&amp;amp;= -\sqrt{2k_nI_D} \frac{V_{R_D}}{I_D} \\
&amp;amp;= -\sqrt{2\mu_n C_{OX}\frac{W}{L}}\frac{V_{R_D}}{\sqrt {I_D}} \\
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;分析-channel-length-modulation&#34;&gt;分析 Channel Length Modulation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
V_{out} = V_{DD} - \frac{1}{2}k_n(V_{in} - V_t)^2 (1 + \lambda V_{out})R_D \\\
\\ \begin{aligned}
A_v &amp;amp;= \frac{\partial V_{out}}{\partial V_{in}}\\
&amp;amp;= - R_Dk_n (V_{in} - V_t)(1 + \lambda V_{out})- \frac{1}{2}k_n R_D(V_{in} - V_t)^2 \lambda\frac{\partial V_{out}}{\partial V_{in}} \\
&amp;amp;= -R_D g_m - I_DR_D \lambda A_v  (近似) \\
&amp;amp;= -\frac{g_m R_D}{1 + R_D \lambda I_D} \\
&amp;amp;= -g_m \frac{r_0R_D}{r_0 + R_D}
\end{aligned}$$&lt;/p&gt;
