&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
I_{D1} &amp;amp;= I_{|D2|} \\
\mu_n C_{OX}(\frac{W}{L})&lt;em&gt;1(V&lt;/em&gt;{GS1} - V_{T1})^2 &amp;amp;= \mu_p C_{OX}(\frac{W}{L})&lt;em&gt;2(V&lt;/em&gt;{GS2} - V_{T2})^2 \\
\therefore A_v &amp;amp;= \frac{|V_{GS2} - V_{T2}|}{V_{GS1} - V_{T1}}
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
