&lt;h2 id=&#34;分析-4&#34;&gt;分析&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$$
\begin{aligned}
V_{out} &amp;amp;= V_{DD} - \frac{1}{2}k_n(V_b -V_{in} -V_t)^2R_D \\
\because \frac{\partial V_t}{\partial V_{in}} &amp;amp;= \frac{\partial V_t}{\partial V_{SB}} = \eta \\
\therefore A_v &amp;amp;= \frac{\partial V_{out}}{\partial V_{in}} \\
&amp;amp;= g_m(1+\eta) R_D
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
