I_{D1} &amp;amp;=  I_1  \\
&amp;amp;=\frac{1}{2}\mu_pC_{OX} (\frac{W}{L})&lt;em&gt;1 (V&lt;/em&gt;{DD} - V_{in} - |V_{T1}|)^2 \\
\therefore V_{in1} &amp;amp;= V_{DD}  -\sqrt{\frac{2I_1}{k_{p}}} -|V_{T1}| \\\
\\ 当V_{in1} &amp;amp;\gt V_{DD}  -\sqrt{\frac{2I_1}{k_{p}}} -|V_{T1}|时: \\
\because I_{D1} &amp;amp;\le I_1  \\
\therefore M_1 &amp;amp;将进入Triode \ Region
\end{aligned}
$$&lt;/p&gt;
